  (1276, 1, 42, 19, 'If ye be true men, let one of your brethren be bound in the house of your prison: go ye, carry corn for the famine of your houses:', '[2] 3~03651~ [4] 6~0259~ 9~0251~ 11~0631~ 14~01004~ 17~04929~: 18~03212~ 20~0935~ 21~07668~ 24~07459~ 27~01004~:'),
