  (27845, 44, 26, 6, 'And now I stand and am judged for the hope of the promise made of God unto our fathers:', '0~2532~ 1~3568~ 3~2476~ 6~2919~ 7~1909~ 9~1680~ 12~1860~ 13~1096~ 14~5259~ 15~2316~ 16~4314~ 18~3962~:'),
