  (6764, 7, 9, 3, 'And his mother''s brethren spake of him in the ears of all the men of Shechem all these words: and their hearts inclined to follow Abimelech; for they said, He is our brother.', '2~0517~ 3~0251~ 4~01696~ 9~0241~ 13~01167~ 15~07927~ 18~01697~: 21~03820~ 22~05186~ 24~0310~ 25~040~; 28~0559~, [30] 32~0251~.'),
