  (10180, 12, 23, 7, 'And he brake down the houses of the sodomites, that were by the house of the LORD, where the women wove hangings for the grove.', '3~05422~ 5~01004~ 8~06945~, [10] 13~01004~ 16~03068~, 19~0802~ 20~0707~ 21~01004~ 24~0842~.'),
