  (24379, 41, 5, 5, 'And always, night and day, he was in the mountains, and in the tombs, crying, and cutting himself with stones.', '0~2532~ 1~1275~, 2~3571~ 3~2532~ 4~2250~, 6~2258~ 7~1722~ 9~3735~, 10~2532~ 11~1722~ 13~3418~, 14~2896~, 15~2532~ 16~2629~ 17~1438~ 19~3037~.'),
