  (4335, 4, 20, 19, 'And the children of Israel said unto him, We will go by the high way: and if I and my cattle drink of thy water, then I will pay for it: I will only, without doing any thing else, go through on my feet.', '2~01121~ 4~03478~ 5~0559~ 10~05927~ 14~04546~: 20~04735~ 21~08354~ 24~04325~, 28~05414~ 29~04377~* [36] 38~01697~ [39] 41~05674~ 44~07272~.'),
