  (29603, 52, 2, 17, 'But we, brethren, being taken from you for a short time in presence, not in heart, endeavoured the more abundantly to see your face with great desire.', '&para; 0~1161~ 1~2249~, 2~80~, 4~642~ 5~575~ 6~5216~ 7~4314~ 9~5610~ 10~2540~ 12~4383~, 13~3756~ 15~2588~, 16~4704~ 19~4056~ 21~1492~ 22~5216~ 23~4383~ 24~1722~ 25~4183~ 26~1939~.'),
