  (5249, 5, 12, 3, 'And ye shall overthrow their altars, and break their pillars, and burn their groves with fire; and ye shall hew down the graven images of their gods, and destroy the names of them out of that place.', '3~05422~ 5~04196~, 7~07665~ 9~04676~, 11~08313~ 13~0842~ 15~0784~; 20~01438~ 23~06456~ 26~0430~, 28~06~ 30~08034~ 36~04725~.'),
