  (26635, 43, 12, 40, 'He hath blinded their eyes, and hardened their heart; that they should not see with their eyes, nor understand with their heart, and be converted, and I should heal them.', '2~5186~ 3~846~ 4~3788~, 5~2532~ 6~4456~ 7~846~ 8~2588~; 9~3363~ 11~1492~ 12~3363~ 13~1492~ [15] 16~3788~, 17~2532~ 18~3539~ [20] 21~2588~, 22~2532~ 24~1994~, 25~2532~ 28~2390~ 29~846~.'),
