  (5973, 6, 6, 18, 'And ye, in any wise keep yourselves from the accursed thing, lest ye make yourselves accursed, when ye take of the accursed thing, and make the camp of Israel a curse, and trouble it.', '4~07535~ 5~08104~ [6] 10~02764~, [14] 15~02763~, 18~03947~ 22~02764~, 24~07760~ 26~04264~ 28~03478~ 30~02764~, 32~05916~'),
