  (7276, 9, 2, 29, 'Wherefore kick ye at my sacrifice and at mine offering, which I have commanded in my habitation; and honourest thy sons above me, to make yourselves fat with the chiefest of all the offerings of Israel my people?', '1~01163~ 5~02077~ 9~04503~, 13~06680~ [14 15] 16~04583~; 18~03513~ 20~01121~ 26~01254~ 29~07225~ 33~04503~ 35~03478~ 37~05971~?'),
