  (2792, 3, 3, 9, 'And he shall offer of the sacrifice of the peace offering an offering made by fire unto the LORD; the fat thereof, and the whole rump, it shall he take off hard by the backbone; and the fat that covereth the inwards, and all the fat that is upon the inwards,', '3~07126~ 6~02077~ 10~08002~ 15~0801~ 18~03068~; 20~02459~ [22] 24~08549~ 25~0451~, 30~05493~ 31~05980~ 34~06096~; 37~02459~ 39~03680~ 41~07130~, 45~02459~ [47] 50~07130~,'),
  (12537, 16, 9, 17, 'And refused to obey, neither were mindful of thy wonders that thou didst among them; but hardened their necks, and in their rebellion appointed a captain to return to their bondage: but thou art a God ready to pardon, gracious and merciful, slow to anger, and of great kindness, and forsookest them not.', '1~03985~ 3~08085~, 6~02142~ 9~06381~ 12~06213~ 16~07185~ 18~06203~, 22~04805~ 23~05414~ 25~07218~ 27~07725~ 30~05659~: [33] 35~0433~ 38~05547~, 39~02587~ 41~07349~, 42~0750~ 44~0639~, 47~07227~ 48~02617~, 50~05800~'),
