  (8938, 11, 6, 34, 'And the two doors were of fir tree: the two leaves of the one door were folding, and the two leaves of the other door were folding.', '2~08147~ 3~01817~ [4 5] 6~01265~ 7~06086~: 9~08147~ 10~06763~ 13~0259~ 14~01817~ [15] 16~01550~, 19~08147~ 20~07050~ 23~08145~ 24~01817~ [25] 26~01550~.'),
