  (28262, 45, 12, 1, 'I beseech you therefore, brethren, by the mercies of God, that ye present your bodies a living sacrifice, holy, acceptable unto God, which is your reasonable service.', '&para; 1~3870~ 2~5209~ 3~3767~, 4~80~, 5~1223~ 7~3628~ 9~2316~, 12~3936~ 13~5216~ 14~4983~ 16~2198~ 17~2378~, 18~40~, 19~2101~ 21~2316~, [22 23] 24~5216~ 25~3050~ 26~2999~.'),
