  (3697, 4, 2, 34, 'And the children of Israel did according to all that the LORD commanded Moses: so they pitched by their standards, and so they set forward, every one after their families, according to the house of their fathers.', '2~01121~ 4~03478~ 5~06213~ 11~03068~ 12~06680~ 13~04872~: 16~02583~ 19~01714~, 24~05265~, 26~0376~ 29~04940~, 33~01004~ 36~01~.'),
