  (30729, 66, 1, 16, 'And he had in his right hand seven stars: and out of his mouth went a sharp twoedged sword: and his countenance was as the sun shineth in his strength.', '0~2532~ 2~2192~ 3~1722~ 4~846~ 5~1188~ 6~5495~ 7~2033~ 8~792~: 9~2532~ 11~1537~ 12~846~ 13~4750~ 14~1607~ 16~3691~ 17~1366~ 18~4501~: 19~2532~ 20~846~ 21~3799~ [22] 23~5613~ 25~2246~ 26~5316~ 27~1722~ 28~846~ 29~1411~.'),
