  (25406, 42, 10, 31, 'And by chance there came down a certain priest that way: and when he saw him, he passed by on the other side.', '0~1161~ 1~2596~ 2~4795~ 5~2597~ 7~5100~ 8~2409~ 9~1565~ 10~1722~* 11~3598~: 12~2532~ 15~1492~ 16~846~, 23~492~.'),
  (22665, 33, 6, 8, 'He hath shewed thee, O man, what is good; and what doth the LORD require of thee, but to do justly, and to love mercy, and to walk humbly with thy God?', '2~05046~ 5~0120~, [7] 8~02896~; 13~03068~ 14~01875~ 19~06213~ 20~04941~, 23~0160~ 24~02617~, 27~03212~ 28~06800~ 31~0430~?'),
