  (20671, 26, 11, 7, 'Therefore thus saith the Lord GOD; Your slain whom ye have laid in the midst of it, they are the flesh, and this city is the caldron: but I will bring you forth out of the midst of it.', '2~0559~ 4~0136~ 5~03069~; 7~02491~ 11~07760~ 14~08432~ [18] 20~01320~, [23 24] 26~05518~: 32~03318~ 36~08432~'),
