  (27176, 44, 7, 44, 'Our fathers had the tabernacle of witness in the wilderness, as he had appointed, speaking unto Moses, that he should make it according to the fashion that he had seen.', '0~2257~ 1~3962~ 2~2258~ 4~4633~ 6~1722~ 7~3142~* 8~1722~ 10~2048~, 11~2531~ 14~1299~, 15~2980~ 17~3475~, 21~4160~ 22~846~ 23~2596~ 26~5179~ 27~3739~ 30~3708~.'),
