  (1282, 1, 42, 25, 'Then Joseph commanded to fill their sacks with corn, and to restore every man''s money into his sack, and to give them provision for the way: and thus did he unto them.', '1~03130~ 2~06680~ 4~04390~ 6~03627~ 8~01250~, 11~07725~ 13~0376~ 14~03701~ 17~08242~, 20~05414~ 22~06720~ 25~01870~: 27~03651~ 29~06213~'),
