  (15311, 19, 87, 1, 'A Psalm or Song for the sons of Korah. His foundation is in the holy mountains.', '&para; [0 1~04210~ [2] 3~07892~ 6~01121~ 8] 8~07141~ 10~03248~ [11] 14~06944~ 15~02042~.'),
