  (1739, 2, 8, 24, 'And the LORD did so; and there came a grievous swarm of flies into the house of Pharaoh, and into his servants'' houses, and into all the land of Egypt: the land was corrupted by reason of the swarm of flies.', '2~03068~ 3~06213~ 7~0935~ 9~03515~ 10~06157~ [11 12] 15~01004~ 17~06547~, [19] 21~05650~ 22~01004~, 27~0776~ 29~04714~: 31~0776~ 33~07843~ 35~06440~ 38~06157~ [39 40]'),
