  (18842, 23, 60, 12, 'For the nation and kingdom that will not serve thee shall perish; yea, those nations shall be utterly wasted.', '2~01471~ 4~04467~ 8~05647~ 11~06~; [13] 14~01471~ 17~02717~ 18~02717~.'),
