  (3196, 3, 15, 23, 'And if it be on her bed, or on any thing whereon she sitteth, when he toucheth it, he shall be unclean until the even.', '[3] [5] 6~04904~, 10~03627~ 13~03427~, 16~05060~ 21~02930~ 24~06153~.'),
