  (24160, 40, 27, 21, 'The governor answered and said unto them, Whether of the twain will ye that I release unto you? They said, Barabbas.', '1~2232~ 2~611~ 3~1161~ 4~2036~ 6~846~, 7~5101~ 8~575~ 10~1417~ 12~2309~ 15~630~ 17~5213~ 18~1161?~* 20~2036~, 21~912~.'),
