  (10200, 12, 23, 27, 'And the LORD said, I will remove Judah also out of my sight, as I have removed Israel, and will cast off this city Jerusalem which I have chosen, and the house of which I said, My name shall be there.', '2~03068~ 3~0559~, 6~05493~ 7~03063~ 12~06440~, 16~05493~ 17~03478~, 21~03988~ 23~05892~ 24~03389~ 28~0977~, 31~01004~ 35~0559~, 37~08034~'),
  (14837, 19, 62, 1, 'To the chief Musician, to Jeduthun, A Psalm of David. Truly my soul waiteth upon God: from him cometh my salvation.', '&para; [0 3~05329~, 5~03038~, 7~04210~ 9] 9~01732~ 12~05315~ 13~01747~ 15~0430~: [18] 20~03444~.'),
  (13693, 18, 34, 1, 'Furthermore Elihu answered and said,', '&para; 1~0453~ 2~06030~ 4~0559~,'),
  (16774, 20, 13, 18, 'Poverty and shame shall be to him that refuseth instruction: but he that regardeth reproof shall be honoured.', '&para; 0~07389~ 2~07036~ [3 5] 8~06544~ 9~04148~: 13~08104~ 14~08433~ 17~03513~.'),
  (2305, 2, 28, 7, 'It shall have the two shoulder pieces thereof joined at the two edges thereof; and so it shall be joined together.', '4~08147~ 5~03802~ 7~02266~ 10~08147~ 11~07098~ [14] 19~02266~.'),
  (20353, 25, 2, 12, 'They say to their mothers, Where is corn and wine? when they swooned as the wounded in the streets of the city, when their soul was poured out into their mothers'' bosom.', '1~0559~ 4~0517~, [6] 7~01715~ 9~03196~? 12~05848~ 15~02491~ 18~07339~ 21~05892~, 24~05315~ 27~08210~ 30~0517~ 31~02436~.'),
  (8618, 10, 22, 8, 'Then the earth shook and trembled; the foundations of heaven moved and shook, because he was wroth.', '2~0776~ 3~01607~ 5~07493~; 7~04146~ 9~08064~ 10~07264~ 12~01607~, 16~02734~.'),
  (16357, 19, 146, 7, 'Which executeth judgment for the oppressed: which giveth food to the hungry. The LORD looseth the prisoners:', '1~06213~ 2~04941~ 5~06231~: 7~05414~ 8~03899~ 11~07457~. 13~03068~ 14~05425~ 16~0631~:'),
  (22471, 30, 6, 12, 'Shall horses run upon the rock? will one plow there with oxen? for ye have turned judgment into gall, and the fruit of righteousness into hemlock:', '1~05483~ 2~07323~ 5~05553~? [7] 8~02790~ [9] 11~01241~? 15~02015~ 16~04941~ 18~07219~, 21~06529~ 23~06666~ 25~03939~:'),
  (16964, 20, 20, 1, 'Wine is a mocker, strong drink is raging: and whosoever is deceived thereby is not wise.', '&para; 0~03196~ [1] 3~03887~, 5~07941~ [6] 7~01993~: 11~07686~ 15~02449~.'),
  (20271, 24, 51, 50, 'Ye that have escaped the sword, go away, stand not still: remember the LORD afar off, and let Jerusalem come into your mind.', '3~06405~ 5~02719~, 7~01980~, 10~05975~: 11~02142~ 13~03068~ 15~07350~, 18~03389~ 19~05927~ 22~03824~.'),
  (10529, 13, 6, 67, 'And they gave unto them, of the cities of refuge, Shechem in mount Ephraim with her suburbs; they gave also Gezer with her suburbs,', '2~05414~ [5] 7~05892~ 9~04733~, 10~07927~ 12~02022~ 13~0669~ 16~04054~; [17 18] 20~01507~ 23~04054~,'),
  (28693, 46, 13, 12, 'For now we see through a glass, darkly; but then face to face: now I know in part; but then shall I know even as also I am known.', '0~1063~ 1~737~ 3~991~ 4~1223~ 6~2072~, 7~135~ 8~1722~;* 9~1161~ 10~5119~ 11~4383~ 12~4314~ 13~4383~: 14~737~ 16~1097~ 17~1537~ 18~3313~; 19~1161~ 20~5119~ 23~1921~ 25~2531~ 26~2532~ 29~1921~.'),
  (8622, 10, 22, 12, 'And he made darkness pavilions round about him, dark waters, and thick clouds of the skies.', '2~07896~ 3~02822~ 4~05521~ 6~05439~ 8~02841~ 9~04325~, [10] 12~05645~ 15~07834~.'),
  (23229, 40, 4, 10, 'Then saith Jesus unto him, Get thee hence, Satan: for it is written, Thou shalt worship the Lord thy God, and him only shalt thou serve.', '0~5119~ 1~3004~ 2~2424~ 4~846~, 7~5217~, 8~4567~: 9~1063~ 12~1125~, 15~4352~ 17~2962~ 18~4675~ 19~2316~, 20~2532~ 21~846~ 22~3441~ 25~3000~.'),
  (20387, 25, 3, 24, 'The LORD is my portion, saith my soul; therefore will I hope in him.', '1~03068~ [2] 4~02506~, 5~0559~ 7~05315~; 11~03176~'),
  (21707, 26, 47, 19, 'And the south side southward, from Tamar even to the waters of strife in Kadesh, the river to the great sea. And this is the south side southward.', '2~05045~ 3~06285~ 4~08486~, 6~08559~ [7] 10~04325~ 12~04808~ 13~04809~* [14] 15~06946~, 17~05158~ 20~01419~ 21~03220~. [23 24] 26~08486~ 27~06285~ 28~05045~.'),
  (10120, 12, 20, 14, 'Then came Isaiah the prophet unto king Hezekiah, and said unto him, What said these men? and from whence came they unto thee? And Hezekiah said, They are come from a far country, even from Babylon.', '1~0935~ 2~03470~ 4~05030~ 6~04428~ 7~02396~, 9~0559~ 13~0559~ 15~0582~? 18~0370~ 19~0935~ 24~02396~ 25~0559~, 28~0935~ 31~07350~ 32~0776~, [33] 35~0894~.'),
  (2710, 2, 39, 41, 'The cloths of service to do service in the holy place, and the holy garments for Aaron the priest, and his sons'' garments, to minister in the priest''s office.', '1~0899~ 3~08278~ 6~08334~ 9~06944~ [10] 13~06944~ 14~0899~ 16~0175~ 18~03548~, 21~01121~ 22~0899~, 28~03547~.'),
  (26873, 43, 19, 33, 'But when they came to Jesus, and saw that he was dead already, they brake not his legs:', '0~1161~ 1~5613~ 3~2064~ 4~1909~ 5~2424~, 7~1492~ 9~846~ 11~2348~ 12~2235~, 14~2608~ 15~3756~ 16~846~ 17~4628~:'),
  (7584, 9, 15, 17, 'And Samuel said, When thou wast little in thine own sight, wast thou not made the head of the tribes of Israel, and the LORD anointed thee king over Israel?', '1~08050~ 2~0559~, [5] 6~06996~ 10~05869~, [11] [14] 16~07218~ 19~07626~ 21~03478~, 24~03068~ 25~04886~ 27~04428~ 29~03478~?'),
