  (17068, 20, 23, 15, 'My son, if thine heart be wise, my heart shall rejoice, even mine.', '1~01121~, 4~03820~ 6~02449~, 8~03820~ 10~08055~, 12~0589~.'),
  (571, 1, 22, 20, 'And it came to pass after these things, that it was told Abraham, saying, Behold, Milcah, she hath also born children unto thy brother Nahor;', '&para; 5~0310~ 7~01697~, 11~05046~ 12~085~, 13~0559~, 15~04435~, 19~03205~ 20~01121~ 23~0251~ 24~05152~;'),
