  (14239, 19, 22, 26, 'The meek shall eat and be satisfied: they shall praise the LORD that seek him: your heart shall live for ever.', '1~06035~ 3~0398~ 6~07646~: 9~01984~ 11~03068~ 13~01875~ 16~03824~ 18~02421~ 20~05703~.'),
  (31061, 66, 20, 7, 'And when the thousand years are expired, Satan shall be loosed out of his prison,', '0~2532~ 1~3752~ 3~5507~ 4~2094~ 6~5055~, 7~4567~ 10~3089~ 12~1537~ 13~846~ 14~5438~,'),
