  (27868, 44, 26, 29, 'And Paul said, I would to God, that not only thou, but also all that hear me this day, were both almost, and altogether such as I am, except these bonds.', '0~1161~ 1~3972~ 2~2036~, 4~2172~ 5~302~* 7~2316~, 9~3756~ 10~3440~ 11~4571~, 12~235~ 13~2532~ 14~3956~ 16~191~ 17~3450~ 19~4594~, 20~1096~ 21~2532~ 22~3641~ 23~1722~,* 24~2532~ 25~4183~ 26~1722~* 27~5108~ 28~2504~ 29~3697~ 30~1510~, 31~3924~ 32~5130~ 33~1199~.'),
