  (5376, 5, 17, 6, 'At the mouth of two witnesses, or three witnesses, shall he that is worthy of death be put to death; but at the mouth of one witness he shall not be put to death.', '2~06310~ 4~08147~ 5~05707~, 7~07969~ 8~05707~, 15~04191~ 19~04191~; [20] 23~06310~ 25~0259~ 26~05707~ 33~04191~.'),
