  (8474, 10, 17, 17, 'Now Jonathan and Ahimaaz stayed by Enrogel; for they might not be seen to come into the city: and a wench went and told them; and they went and told king David.', '1~03083~ 3~0290~ 4~05975~ 6~05883~; 9~03201~ 12~07200~ 14~0935~ 17~05892~: 20~08198~ 21~01980~ 23~05046~ 27~03212~ 29~05046~ 30~04428~ 31~01732~.'),
