  (23976, 40, 24, 9, 'Then shall they deliver you up to be afflicted, and shall kill you: and ye shall be hated of all nations for my name''s sake.', '0~5119~ 3~3860~ 4~5209~ 5~3860~ 6~1519~ 8~2347~, 9~2532~ 11~615~ 12~5209~: 13~2532~ 16~2071~ 17~3404~ 18~5259~ 19~3956~ 20~1484~ 21~1223~ 22~3450~ 24~3686~.'),
