  (12699, 16, 13, 19, 'And it came to pass, that when the gates of Jerusalem began to be dark before the sabbath, I commanded that the gates should be shut, and charged that they should not be opened till after the sabbath: and some of my servants set I at the gates, that there should no burden be brought in on the sabbath day.', '8~08179~ 10~03389~ 14~06751~ 15~06440~ 17~07676~, 19~0559~ 22~01817~ 25~05462~, 27~0559~ 33~06605~ 35~0310~ 37~07676~: [39] 42~05288~ 43~05975~ 47~08179~, [48] 52~04853~ 55~0935~ 58~07676~ 59~03117~.'),
