  (28064, 45, 5, 1, 'Therefore being justified by faith, we have peace with God through our Lord Jesus Christ:', '&para; 0~3767~ 2~1344~ 3~1537~ 4~4102~, 6~2192~ 7~1515~ 8~4314~ 9~2316~ 10~1223~ 11~2257~ 12~2962~ 13~2424~ 14~5547~:'),
