  (3454, 3, 24, 3, 'Without the veil of the testimony, in the tabernacle of the congregation, shall Aaron order it from the evening unto the morning before the LORD continually: it shall be a statute for ever in your generations.', '0~02351~ 2~06532~ 5~05715~, 8~0168~ 11~04150~, 13~0175~ 14~06186~ 18~06153~ 21~01242~ 22~06440~ 24~03068~ 25~08548~: [26 28] 30~02708~ 32~05769~ 35~01755~.'),
