  (6880, 7, 12, 4, 'Then Jephthah gathered together all the men of Gilead, and fought with Ephraim: and the men of Gilead smote Ephraim, because they said, Ye Gileadites are fugitives of Ephraim among the Ephraimites, and among the Manassites.', '1~03316~ 3~06908~ 6~0582~ 8~01568~, 10~03898~ 12~0669~: 15~0582~ 17~01568~ 18~05221~ 19~0669~, 22~0559~, 24~01568~ [25] 26~06412~ 28~0669~ 29~08432~ 31~0669~, [32] 33~08432~ 35~04519~.'),
  (25716, 42, 18, 14, 'I tell you, this man went down to his house justified rather than the other: for every one that exalteth himself shall be abased; and he that humbleth himself shall be exalted.', '1~3004~ 2~5213~, 4~3778~ 6~2597~ 7~1519~ 8~846~ 9~3624~ 10~1344~ [11] 12~2228~ 14~1565~: 15~3754~ 17~3956~ 19~5312~ 20~1438~ 23~5013~; 24~1161~ 27~5013~ 28~1438~ 31~5312~.'),
