  (1301, 1, 43, 6, 'And Israel said, Wherefore dealt ye so ill with me, as to tell the man whether ye had yet a brother?', '1~03478~ 2~0559~, [6] 7~07489~ [10] 12~05046~ 14~0376~ 20~0251~?'),
