  (27649, 44, 20, 7, 'And upon the first day of the week, when the disciples came together to break bread, Paul preached unto them, ready to depart on the morrow; and continued his speech until midnight.', '&para; 0~1161~ 1~1722~ 3~3391~ [4] 7~4521~, 10~3101~ 12~4863~ 14~2806~ 15~740~, 16~3972~ 17~1256~ 19~846~, 20~3195~ 22~1826~ 25~1887~; 26~5037~ 27~3905~ 29~3056~ 30~3360~ 31~3317~.'),
