  (24799, 41, 14, 34, 'And saith unto them, My soul is exceeding sorrowful unto death: tarry ye here, and watch.', '0~2532~ 1~3004~ 3~846~, 4~3450~ 5~5590~ 6~2076~ 8~4036~ 9~2193~ 10~2288~: 12~3306~ 13~5602~, 14~2532~ 15~1127~.'),
