  (27490, 44, 15, 32, 'And Judas and Silas, being prophets also themselves, exhorted the brethren with many words, and confirmed them.', '1~2455~ 2~2532~ 3~4609~, 4~5607~ 5~4396~ 6~2532~ 7~846~, 8~3870~ 10~80~ 11~1223~ 12~4183~ 13~3056~, 14~2532~ 15~1991~ [16]'),
